1
00:00:15,615 --> 00:00:16,983
Chen Tianyou,

2
00:00:20,787 --> 00:00:22,522
why haven't you been replying to my texts?

3
00:00:24,224 --> 00:00:25,492
Did you change your number?

4
00:00:28,795 --> 00:00:30,196
No, I didn't.

5
00:00:30,196 --> 00:00:32,065
If you call, I'll answer.

6
00:00:39,372 --> 00:00:41,307
I waited seven years for him.

7
00:00:46,546 --> 00:00:48,114
I wasted the best years of my life

8
00:00:48,114 --> 00:00:50,016
on that one person.

9
00:00:50,784 --> 00:00:51,785
Tell me,

10
00:00:54,087 --> 00:00:55,922
was it really worth the wait?

11
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,108
You still have it?

12
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:17,277
Not only that,

13
00:01:19,045 --> 00:01:19,979
I'm still wearing it.

14
00:01:21,581 --> 00:01:22,715
But this morning,

15
00:01:22,715 --> 00:01:24,017
I accidentally broke it.

16
00:01:25,585 --> 00:01:27,420
I thought it was a sign to finally let go.

17
00:01:34,861 --> 00:01:35,695
You said

18
00:01:37,163 --> 00:01:38,465
the person in my heart,

19
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,068
the one looking back at me,

20
00:01:44,971 --> 00:01:45,972
would never be you.

21
00:01:48,975 --> 00:01:50,109
So you realized.

22
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,881
Are you crazy?

23
00:01:55,915 --> 00:01:57,383
Why would you hide a message like that?

24
00:01:58,218 --> 00:01:59,586
What if I never found it?

25
00:02:00,019 --> 00:02:01,754
Why couldn't you say this to my face?

26
00:02:03,690 --> 00:02:04,557
I was scared.

27
00:02:06,259 --> 00:02:07,260
Scared you'd reject me,

28
00:02:08,528 --> 00:02:09,395
but even more scared

29
00:02:11,965 --> 00:02:13,032
that you'd say yes.

30
00:02:28,248 --> 00:02:29,482
I'm asking you one last time.

31
00:02:31,151 --> 00:02:32,585
Do you want to be with me?

32
00:03:08,154 --> 00:03:08,988
Cut!

33
00:03:10,256 --> 00:03:11,090
That's a wrap!

34
00:03:12,592 --> 00:03:13,493
Congratulations!

35
00:03:13,893 --> 00:03:15,328
Congrats to the "Black &amp; White" team!

36
00:03:15,328 --> 00:03:15,929
We're all done!

37
00:03:15,929 --> 00:03:16,462
Thank you!

38
00:03:16,462 --> 00:03:16,963
Thanks, everyone!

39
00:03:16,963 --> 00:03:17,764
Thank you!

40
00:03:17,897 --> 00:03:18,898
Great job, everyone!

41
00:03:20,133 --> 00:03:21,100
I think this is gonna be a hit.

42
00:03:21,768 --> 00:03:23,503
Trust me, it's a guaranteed success.

43
00:03:23,503 --> 00:03:25,171
By the way, don't forget my bonus.

44
00:03:25,171 --> 00:03:26,272
I'm expecting a cut of the profits!
